title: Patrik Prikryl
text:
Patrik Prikryl (born 19 September 1992) is a <a href="Slovakia">Slovak</a> <a href="Association%20football">football</a> defender who currently plays for <a href="MFK%20Dukla%20Bansk%C3%A1%20Bystrica">Dukla Banská Bystrica</a>.
Club career.
1. FC Tatran Prešov.
Prikryl made his professional <a href="Slovak%20First%20Football%20League">Fortuna Liga</a> debut for <a href="1.%20FC%20Tatran%20Pre%C5%A1ov">Tatran Prešov</a> against <a href="FK%20%C5%BDeleziarne%20Podbrezov%C3%A1">Železiarne Podbrezová</a> on 18 February 2018.
